# Cloudflare applies these headers to every route.
# Content-Security-Policy beyond frame-ancestors is intentionally not set here — getting it
# right requires auditing every inline script (incl. Astro ClientRouter) and the Cloudflare
# Analytics beacon. The frame-ancestors directive below is the critical one for the Studio
# iframe-pane preview. Revisit a full CSP post-launch.
#
# frame-ancestors: allows the Sanity Studio (both the hosted Sanity.io deploy and local dev
# servers) to iframe the live site for the iframe-pane preview plugin.
# 'self' lets the site embed itself. Modern browsers prefer CSP frame-ancestors over
# X-Frame-Options when both are present.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://*.sanity.studio https://www.sanity.io https://*.sanity.io http://localhost:3333 http://localhost:3334
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
